   [gpp.jpg]
   Best in the U.S. !!!
   The GPP results are in, and Maricopa County came out on top! In a
   comprehensive evaluation of local governments, only two counties in the
   nation received the top score of A-. Maricopa County is proud to serve
   its citizens as one of the two most effective county governments in the
   U.S.
   Click here for more information and evaluation details.

